---
title: Double Lamb Rump & Roast Veggie Salad with Indian Coconut Sauce
description: It's roast lamb, but not as you know it! We're using our mild yet flavourful North Indian spice blend to lift succulent lamb rump
to new heights. With a generous helping of roasted veggies, it's all you need to create a meal fit for royalty!
